CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Lead Real Estate Co., Ltd, together with its subsidiaries, develops and sells luxury residential properties. The company develops single-family homes and condominiums. It operates hotels in Tokyo and leases apartment building units in Japan and Dallas, Texas. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
